# Operator Matematika

Oerator                                     Keterangan

+                                           Penjumlahan
-                                           Pengurangan
*                                           Perkalian
/                                           Pembagian
%                                           Sisa pembagian

# Augmented Assignments

Operasi Matematika                                  Augmented Assignments
a = a + 10                                          a += 10
a = a - 10                                          a -= 10
a = a * 10                                          a *= 10
a = a / 10                                          a /= 10
a = a % 10                                          a %= 10

# Unary Operator

Operator                                        Keterangan

++                                              a = a + 1
--                                              a = a - 1
-                                               Negative
+                                               Positive
!                                               Boolean kebalikan